subject: Tennis
United States Open (Tennis)
lead_paragraph: No. 2 Rafael Nadal beat No. 1 Novak Djokovic, 6-2, 3-6, 6-4, 6-1, for his second United States Open singles title. They played for the title for the third time in four years.
